CBI’s Adult Program offers sailing, windsurfing, paddleboarding, and kayaking to adults 18 years and older. The Adult Program runs from April 1 to October 31, seven days per week. Membership includes instruction (formal classes and informal on-water instruction), access to the dock and boats, a ratings system, and unlimited use of boats during Adult Program hours.

For Junior Program memberships;
